ActiveX ActiveX control ActiveX l k thut c component ha trong software m microsoft pht trin. N ch yu thc hin vic m rng chc nng tng thch trn internet

ActiveX control c s dng bng cch down t web server thng qua internet hoc intranet , ri add thm chc nng cho IE ca Web browser cng ca Microsoft.

ActiveX control c cng khai bi nhiu cty, khng ch microsoft. Nhiu loi active phong ph nh:
ActiveX play trn web page m thanh hoc hnh nh. Hoc ActiveX control thc hin tra i thng tin communication gia server v client.

Vic download program ri chy trn WEB browser c v hi ging Java applet nhng ActiveX control c hnh thnh trn native code nn hot ng s nhanh hn Java applet. Ngoi ra, n c th s dng tt c cc chc nng m Windows c sn.
Nhng mt tri l scurity ca n thp hn so vi Java applet. Rt c kh nng l my tnh s b ph hy bi 1 ActiveX control c no .

X ActiveX ActiveX l tn gi chung cho nhm k thut lin quan n internet do cty Microsoft pht trin. ActiveX khng phi l tn gi c nh cho k thut hay sn phm no
ActiveX c to nn bi cc k thut m c th s dng trn Internet Explorer(IE) ca Web browser, hoc Internet Information Server(IIS) ca Web server.

K thut ActiveX Web browser c th k n nh
ActiveX control,
ActiveX document (gi, nhn file c to bi word, excel trong phn mm office to bi chnh microsoft, ri chuyn n web browser v hin th ra),
ActiveX Script (s dng cc ngn ng script nh VBScript v JavaScript lm cho Web page hot ng ect v.v...

K thut ActiveX Web server c th k n nh:
Active Server Pages(ASP) : chy cc ngn ng script nh VBScript, JavaScript , sau ch gi n browser kt qu x l
Internet Server API(ISAPI): t Web server gi application software khc thc hin x l.

Interface (I/F) Giao din I/F l interface hoc l tiu chun ng gia 2 i tng no , lm trung gian chuyn thng tin.
Trong IT th chia ra lm 3 phn ln l Hardware interface, software interface, User interface.
Hardware interface l qui tc thng tin, kt ni cc thit b . N qui nh v hnh dng ca connector, hoc tn hiu in.
Ty theo hnh thc chuyn data trong ni b my tnh, hay gia my tnh v thit b ngoi vi, hay gia cc my tnh vi nhau ... m s c cc interface khc nhau.

Software interface qui nh trnh t, hnh thc trao i data gia cc chng trnh. c bit l qui c gi chc nng no ca OS v Component (l sofware c component ha) bn ngoi s dng --> gi l API. Hnh thc file ect... theo ngha rng th cng chnh la I/F nhng thng thng th hiu I/F la API.

User interface qui nh cch computer hin th thng tin ra vi user v ngc li l cch user input thng tin . Trc y th trong thi gian di hnh thc truyn thng chracter c s dng nhng do tnhang ca my tnhc nng ln, my tnh c ph cp ha th hnh thc graphical user interface (hin th graphic, thao tc chut) c s dng rng ri hn.

La` software de chay cac thiet bi lan can. Day la software lam cau noi de OS co the chay duoc cac thiet bi lan can. Cung co khi chi goi bang ten ngan gon la Driver (). Tuy theo dac tinh cua thiet bi, va cach dieu khien cua he thong ma co su khac nhau. Khong phai 1 minh OS se support tat ca cac san pham. Vi the khi maker cung cap cac thiet bi phu tro thi cung cung cap luon device driver de dieu khien. User se install driver do vao may tinh de su dung. Device driver can phu hop voi tung OS nen cung co nhieu truong hop khong co driver cho cac OS doi thap. Development language Ngon ngu lap trinh duoc viet dua tren ngon ngu ma con nguoi co the hieu duoc nhu bang tieng Anh chang han, vi the neu cu de nguyen nhu vay thi may tinh khong the hieu duoc. De may tinh co the chay duoc source code da duoc viet ra bang ngon ngu lap trinh thi can thuc hien xu ly Asemble hoac Compile de dich sang chuoi ngon ngu may tinh Object code () .

Gan day, xuat hien nhieu hon ngon ngu lap trinh don gian, toc do xu ly co the cham nhung lam cho viec code cac chuong trinh qui mo nho tro nen don gian --> cai do goi la Script language.

Ngon ngu lap trinh tuy vao muc do de hieu cua no doi voi con nguoi ma chia ra lam 1 so loai: assembler language high-level language ngon ngu the he thu 4 4 . Ngon ngucang kho thi lai cang gan voi ngon ngu may tinh , cang dieu khien duoc may tinh truc tiep hon . Ngon ngu gan voi ngon ngu tu nhien cua con nguoi thi goi la Ngon ngu bac cao ngon ngu lap trinh cang gan voi ngon ngu may tinh thi goi la Ngon ngu bac thap .

Trong ngon ngu lap trinh co 1 so loai khac nhau , tuy nhien do tinh chat de viet, de migrate, co the code duoc ca nhung xu ly o tang sau --> ngon ngu C, C++ va cac ngon ngu phai' sinh tu do hien dang duoc su dung pho bien.

Nhung nam gan day, dang ngon ngu Script nhu Perl duoc su dung de viet system cho Web base , hoac ngon ngu phai' sinh co kha nang migrate cao hon ngon ngu goc cua no va`
co nhieu thanh phan mang tinh Object nhu ngon ngu Java dang tro nen pho bien.

Machine language Ngon ngu may tinh la ngon ngu ma may tinh co the truc tiep doc hieu duoc. Duoc the hien bang cac con so, con nguoi khong the hieu duoc 1 cach don gian noi dung trong do.

Cung co the inout truc tiep machine language de chay chuong trinh, nhung thuong thi khi viet chuong trinh voi machine language nguoi ta se su dung asembly language (mnemonic) tuong thich 1-1 voi lenh cua may tinh.
